In a method it runs like this:

```
interceptorMethod () {
	try {
		ContextHolder.init();
        doSomething();
	} finally {
	    ContextHolder.clear();
	}
}
```
And ContextHolder is like this:
```
ContextHolder {
    ThreadLocal&lt;Integer&gt; data1 = new ...
	ThreadLocal&lt;Integer&gt; data2 = new ...
    init(int d1, int d2) {
	   data1.set(d1)
